                                 ----------------------- ----------------------  -------------------------------              
                                  |       |        |         |       |                  |                  |
                            ArrayList LinkedList  Vector   Hashset  SortedSet(I)      Dequeue(I)       Priority Queue
                                                              |          |               |
                                                          linkedHashset  Treeset      ArrayQueue               




                                                  Map(Interface)
                                                         |
